org.opendaylight.controller.config.api.runtime

Interface RootRuntimeBeanRegistrator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RootRuntimeBeanRegistratorImpl

    public interface RootRuntimeBeanRegistrator
extends java.io.Closeable
    Entry point for runtime bean functionality. Allows for registering root runtime bean, returning an object that allows for hierarchical registrations.

      • close

        void close()
        Close all runtime beans. This method is idempotent. It is allowed to use this instance to register root or create new child registrators afterwards, but it is not allowed to use closed registrations.
